<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Freshman Guide</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/guid.css">
</head>

<body>

    <div class="bg-glow bg-glow-1"></div>
    <div class="bg-glow bg-glow-2"></div>
    <div class="paper-grid"></div>

    <div class="close-btn" onclick="window.location.href='/cylinder#cylinder'">✖</div>

    <main class="guide-page">

        <section class="guide-hero">
            <p class="mini-title">STUDY BUDDY STARTER PACK</p>
            <h1>Freshman Guide</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">
                Tap the sticky note to reveal your next college survival tip.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="guide-layout">

            <div class="stack-wrap">

                <div class="stack" id="stack">

                    <div class="note" onclick="next()">
                        <span class="note-number">01</span>
                        <b>Welcome 🎓</b>
                        <p>
                            Starting college can feel overwhelming, but everyone is new like you.
                            Take your time, explore, and remember that you belong here.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="note" onclick="next()">
                        <span class="note-number">02</span>
                        <b>Go to Class 📚</b>
                        <p>
                            Showing up is half the success. Even on lazy days, attendance matters.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="note" onclick="next()">
                        <span class="note-number">03</span>
                        <b>Make Friends 🤝</b>
                        <p>
                            Talk to people around you. A simple conversation can turn into a great friendship.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="note" onclick="next()">
                        <span class="note-number">04</span>
                        <b>Ask for Help ❓</b>
                        <p>
                            If something is unclear, ask early. It saves time and stress later.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="note" onclick="next()">
                        <span class="note-number">05</span>
                        <b>Take Care ❤️</b>
                        <p>
                            Sleep well, eat well, and do not ignore your health.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="note" onclick="next()">
                        <span class="note-number">06</span>
                        <b>Stay Organized 🗂️</b>
                        <p>
                            Keep track of deadlines, notes, and tasks to avoid last-minute pressure.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="note" onclick="next()">
                        <span class="note-number">07</span>
                        <b>Manage Time ⏰</b>
                        <p>
                            Balance studying, relaxing, and social life. Time management is key.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="note" onclick="next()">
                        <span class="note-number">08</span>
                        <b>Try New Things 🌟</b>
                        <p>
                            Join clubs, attend events, and explore new experiences.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="note" onclick="next()">
                        <span class="note-number">09</span>
                        <b>Don't Fear Mistakes 💡</b>
                        <p>
                            Mistakes are part of learning. Focus on improving, not being perfect.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="note" onclick="next()">
                        <span class="note-number">10</span>
                        <b>Enjoy the Journey 🚀</b>
                        <p>
                            College is more than grades. Make memories and enjoy every moment.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                </div>

                <div class="guide-nav" id="guideNav">
                    <div class="nav-top">
                        <span id="stepText">Tip 1 of 10</span>
                        <span id="percentText">10%</span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="progress-bar">
                        <div class="progress-fill" id="progressFill"></div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="dots" id="dots">
                        <div class="dot"></div>
                        <div class="dot"></div>
                        <div class="dot"></div>
                        <div class="dot"></div>
                        <div class="dot"></div>
                        <div class="dot"></div>
                        <div class="dot"></div>
                        <div class="dot"></div>
                        <div class="dot"></div>
                        <div class="dot"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p class="hint">✦ Tap the sticky note to continue</p>

                <div class="final" id="final">
                    <div class="final-icon">🚀</div>
                    <h2>You are ready!</h2>
                    <p>
                        You finished the freshman guide. Keep going, stay curious,
                        and make your first year count.
                    </p>
                    <button onclick="restart()">Read Again</button>
                </div>

            </div>

        </section>

    </main>

    <script src="/javaScript/freshguide.js"></script>

</body>
</html>